            "body": "Right, but it should be possible to do this in a simpler way, that is simple enough to put in the official documentation. People aren't going to Do The Right Thing if it takes them too much time. Also, I think your example still doesn't actually clean the cython-built files, since setuptools isn't aware of that. The proper way to fix this would be to do hook into the extension points that setuptools provides. I forget what they are exactly, but they do have documentation on this.",
